-- B2.2 (Stage 2): backfill every org_id to the Proxy org and set the column
-- default to the Proxy org id. The default is load-bearing: existing app code
-- inserts rows without org_id, so Stage 3's NOT NULL would break production
-- writes without it. New rows belong to Proxy until the app passes org ids
-- explicitly (Sub-phase B3 / Phase 3).
-- document_templates is intentionally NOT backfilled: org_id = null there
-- means system template shared across tenants.

